metadata.name: Shax VS Terrell - No Sacrifices 2 day
metadata.description:
This work is my entry to the #Born2DieContest

In this piece Skelliot Deville is dead, the sacrifical lamb is safe. Who is the savior? Nobody knows who he is or where he came from. From his mouth only a short and strong sentence was heard. NO SACRIFICES 2DAY
